textBody:
Lanista[http://orthoptera.speciesfile.org/Common/basic/Taxa.aspx?TaxonNameID=1133960 Orthoptera species file (retrieved 3 January 2018)] is a genus of African bush-cricket (Orthoptera: Tettigoniidae) in the subfamily Conocephalinae.

Species

* Lanista affinis Bolívar, 1906
* Lanista annulicornis (Walker, 1869)
* Lanista crassicollis Bolívar, 1906
* Lanista varelai Bolívar, 1906
